categories: Category:LEGO Star Wars: The Freemaker Adventures voice actors

nodes.text: Dana Snyder (born November 14, 1973) is an American actor, stand-up comedian, and writer who voiced Graballa the Hutt in LEGO Star Wars: The Freemaker Adventures. His other projects have included Aqua Teen Hunger Force, the Aqua Teen Hunger Force Colon Movie Film for Theaters, and the animated TV series Chowder. During an interview with The Star Wars Show host Anthony Carboni, Snyder likened his character Graballa to a "Brooklyn mobster guy whose brother is the head of the family." He likened his rendition of Graballa to a Hutt speaking a "Southern accent."
